Interface HasAllSelectHandlers<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - select value type
    All Superinterfaces:
    HasHandlers, HasHiddenHandlers, HasHideHandlers, HasLoadedHandlers, HasRefreshedHandlers, HasRenderedHandlers, HasShowHandlers, HasShownHandlers, HasValueChangeHandlers<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MultipleSelect, Select, SelectBase

    public interface HasAllSelectHandlers<T>
extends HasLoadedHandlers, HasValueChangeHandlers<T>, HasShowHandlers, HasShownHandlers, HasHideHandlers, HasHiddenHandlers, HasRenderedHandlers, HasRefreshedHandlers
    Convenience interface used to implement all select handlers at once.
